value.Directions: From Lanesboro, take County Road 8 west. Take Ox Trail Road right at the edge of town. Take Grit Road at the split. Stay on Grit Road for 1.5 miles and property is located on North side of Grit Road.
value.PublicRemarks:
Here is a rare opportunity to purchase an excellent-sized acreage just minutes from historic downtown Lanesboro. The 1996 custom-built home has awe-inspiring views as it sits on the bluff top overlooking the South Branch of the Root River and the Root River State Trail. There is so much to do in this area. It's an excellent spot to be your forever home, vacation home, or used as an investment for a VRBO or Air B&B. The Old Barn Resort and Golf Course are only minutes away; downtown Lanesboro is also only minutes away for local shopping, dining, entertainment, biking, canoeing, rafting, and more. The South Branch of the Root River and the Root River State Trail runs along the property's West side, allowing you to fish within walking distance of your backdoor. The paved Root River State Trail meanders 42 miles alongside the Root River from Fountain to Houston for your biking, walking, and running experience. 
The home features a stone front and vinyl-coated steel siding.

The lower level is perfect for multi-generational living with an additional dwelling unit complete with its own kitchen, private 3/4 bath, storage area and large bedroom! This lovely home features newer widows, newer roof, newer furnace, brand new garage door and brand new front entrance door.

value.PublicRemarks: Welcome to this beautiful split-level home in the highly sought-after area of Albertville. As you approach the home, you'll immediately notice its attractive curb appeal and welcoming front entrance. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a spacious foyer. The upper level of the home features a spacious and inviting living room, along with new hardwood floors, granite countertops, and Black Stainless Steel appliances. The 4 season porch provides an excellent area for you to enjoy the extra living space and spacious backyard. The lower level of the home offers a versatile family room, ideal for hosting movie nights, game days, or creating a cozy entertainment space. Additionally, there are 2 bedrooms on this level, perfect for a home office, gym, or guest suite. conveniently located in Albertville, this home offers easy access to a wide range of amenities, including shopping centers, restaurants, parks, and recreational facilities.
